name: Olivia Boler
text: My husband and I came here for our honeymoon. It was magical, we took a dip in the pond and now we have green skin :) I would 100% recommend coming here with your loved ones. Very beautiful.

name: Mr Pz
text: I love the tours and the glow in the dark fish in the surrounding areas. Yay!

name: 3d among us
text: Great nuclear plant! and no coal! As soon as I saw it I felt happy :)

name: James Woods
text: It’s a nuclear plant that doesn’t make power.  Maybe it’s just another Hollywood prop!

name: Dan Ferguson
text: For a nuclear plant that has never been opened, I'd say it's one of the best...? Nothing says welcome to Hollywood like than two giant nuclear reactors!

name: Bart Withrow
text: TVA seems to be getting greedy. Just sell it let him finish it and buy it back.
